object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id) as batch_id
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
		    AND target_schema_name = '$$refined_schema'
)
select
CASE WHEN aan.note_type = 'N' THEN 'N - Notes' WHEN aan.note_type = 'F' THEN 'F - Formerly' WHEN aan.note_type = 'T' THEN 'T - Termination' ELSE aan.note_type END as note_type,
aan.originating_source_name,
aan.originating_load_type,
aan.adm_agency_notes_row_status,
aan.note_id,
aan.created_date,
aan.modified_date,
aan.note_text,
ata.agency_num,
tgt.agency_note_in_adm_id as tgt_agency_note_in_adm_id,
tgt.agency_note_in_adm_row_source_system_key as tgt_agency_note_in_adm_row_source_system_key,
tgt.agency_note_in_adm_row_md5checksum as tgt_agency_note_in_adm_row_md5checksum,
cb.batch_id
from
$$staging_schema.adm_agency_notes aan
left join (
select
agency_num,
agency_nup
from
$$staging_schema.adm_t_agency
where
adm_t_agency_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
) ata on
aan.agency_nup = ata.agency_nup
left join $$refined_schema.agency_notes_in_adm tgt
on aan.note_id = tgt.agency_note_in_adm_row_source_system_key
cross join current_batch cb
where
aan.adm_agency_notes_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'

fields.expression:
MD5('note_type' || note_type ||
'originating_source_name' || originating_source_name ||
'originating_load_type' || originating_load_type ||
'adm_agency_notes_row_status' || adm_agency_notes_row_status ||
'created_date' || to_char(created_date,'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss') ||
'modified_date' || to_char(modified_date,'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss') ||
'note_text' || note_text ||
'agency_num' || agency_num
)
